During your visit to our site, we may collect certain data about you via the deposit of cookies. These cookies allow us to optimize your shopping experience, personalize content and ads, and analyze site traffic.

Required

Necessary cookies are essential to enable our website to be usable by enabling basic functions such as page navigation and access to secure areas of the website. Without these cookies, the website cannot function properly.

Preferences

Preference cookies are used by the website to store information that changes the way the website behaves based on your personal preferences.

Statistics

Statistical cookies allow website owners to anonymously collect and report information about how visitors interact with their website. This data collection helps website owners understand how to improve their website to provide a better user experience.

Marketing

Marketing cookies are used to track visitors across different websites. The goal is to display advertisements that are relevant and interesting to each individual user, which is beneficial for third-party advertisers and website publishers. By tracking users' browsing habits, advertisers can display targeted advertisements that are more likely to grab their attention and lead them to make a purchase or take a specific action on their website.
